\dt \e{Main Canvas}

\dd \G{png.d/maincanvas.png} 

\u000

\dd Main drawing area with rulers along each side.

\u000

\dd The \f{Main Canvas} is where all tracks and objects (and optional background image) are drawn.

\u000

