\dd Change block gaps (\K{cmdAcclKeys}) - \e{Shift+Right-Click}

\dd If at endpoint: disconnect track, otherwise: split track - \e{Left-Click}

\u000


\dt \i{Straight Track} Command (\K{cmdStraight}) - \e{Ctrl+G}

